.TP
\f3document.browse.margin_width\f2 <num>\f1 (default: 3)
Horizontal text margin.
.PD
.RE
.TP
\f3document.browse.refresh\f2 [0|1]\f1 (default: 1)
Automatically follow document-specified refresh directives ('<meta>
