visible. Requires the underlining is enabled for the terminal.
.TP
\f3ui.dialogs.underline_button_shortcuts\f2 [0|1]\f1 (default: 0)
Whether to underline button shortcuts to make them more
visible. Requires the underlining is enabled for the terminal.
